WEBVTT

00:00:00.917 --> 00:00:03.643
Je unafikiri vitu tunavyojenga leo

00:00:03.667 --> 00:00:05.833
vitahesabika kama maajabu miaka ijayo?

00:00:07.042 --> 00:00:08.684
Tafakari kuhusu Stonehenge,

00:00:08.708 --> 00:00:10.226
Mapiramidi,

00:00:10.250 --> 00:00:12.917
Machu Picchu na Kisiwa cha Easter

00:00:14.167 --> 00:00:17.083
Vyote hivi ni tofauti sana
na vile tunavyofanya leo,

00:00:18.333 --> 00:00:19.792
na yale mawe makubwa,

00:00:19.792 --> 00:00:20.792
yakiwa yamepangwa katika hali ya kiutata
hali ngumu kuelewa



00:00:26.292 --> 00:00:29.934
na mabaki yake yote ya ujenzi 


00:00:29.958 --> 00:00:31.601
yakifutwa,